@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Visa";
}

@section MyLinkCSS {
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/visa.css" asp-append-version="true" />
}

<section class="Dream-Section">
    <p class="Dream-Section-Header h1  text-uppercase text-center ">
        Why we need visa in our trips?
    </p>
</section>

<section class="Choose-Section">
    <p class="h1 mt-4 text-capitalize text-center ">
        Visa Information
    </p>
    <p class="lead px-5">
        When planning your travels, understanding visa requirements is a critical step to ensure smooth and
        hassle-free journeys. A visa is an official document issued by a country that grants you permission to
        enter, stay, or leave their territory for a specific period. It is typically attached to your passport
        and is essential for maintaining security and legal protocols for international travel.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="Why-Section">
    <p class="h2 mt-4 text-capitalize text-center ">
        Why Do Travelers Need a Visa?
    </p>
    <div class="Why-Section-Container">


        <img class="Why-Section-Img" src="~/media/Visa/why_visa.jpg" alt="">

        <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                        Legal Entry
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                     data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        A visa ensures that you meet the entry requirements of the destination country,
                        preventing unauthorized entry.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                        Security
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        It allows governments to monitor who is entering their country, ensuring the safety of
                        their citizens and visito
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        Purpose of Visit
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Different visas are issued based on the purpose of travel—tourism, business, study, or
                        work.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


    </div>

</section>